300 REM READCHAR ROUTINE SRC:
400 REM https://www.1000bit.it/support/manuali/apple/technotes/misc/tn.misc.10.html
500 REM ==============
600 REM INITIALIZATION
700 D$ = CHR$(4)
800 Z = 10 : I = 1
900 DIM LINES$(Z)
1000 MX = 0 : MY = 0 : REM MAP ROOMS COORDINATES
1100 RW = 9 : RH = 4 : REM ROOM SIZE
