14500 GOTO 10400

14600 REM MAP CHARACTER READ ROUTINE
14700 REM PEEK(36) AND POS(0) ARE NOT WORKING IN 80 COL, SO BELOW WE ACCESS DIFFERENT ADDRESSES TO BE SURE
14800 POKE 1147,X : POKE 1403,X : POKE 36,X : REM POKE 1531,Y : POKE 37,Y
